User signs up
        ↓
role = CUSTOMER by default
        ↓
Logged-in user applies to become service provider
        ↓
ServiceProvider profile/request is created with status PENDING
        ↓
Admin approves
        ↓
ServiceProvider status = APPROVED
User role = SERVICE_PROVIDER


--------------------------------------------------------------
USER applies
   ↓
Provider created (PENDING)
   ↓
Admin dashboard lists PENDING providers
   ↓
Admin opens provider details
   ↓
Approve / Reject
   ↓
Status updated
